data.description: This charming one-story home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with the added bonus of a versatile extra space that could potentially serve as a 4th bedroom or an income-generating opportunity. The generously-sized backyard offers an oversized lot, providing ample room for a pool or hosting memorable family gatherings. The property boasts a convenient circular driveway, offering parking space for multiple cars, and includes the added benefits of Impact windows and gas utilities. Its prime LOCATION is a major highlight, as it is conveniently close to everything, including stadiums, casinos, and express highways. Don't miss out on this opportunity – SEND YOUR OFFER today!"
